Breda-based CaitC has not been around for long, but she already made quite an impact on the scene. While dancefloor drum and bass is her main genre, she likes to experiment a little with other genres as well. This results in fascinating sets, with the crowd swept off their feet.

Her vivid presence didn’t go unnoticed, because earlier this year, CaitC should have made her international debut, at the Belgian ‘High Rollerz: Carnivore & Friends’. Unfortunately, this has been postponed due to Coronavirus, but if it depends on her, she’s ready to conquer the world!

She has been quiet over the last couple of weeks but that doesn’t mean she has been sitting still. With her newfound passion for producing she is excited to show you what she has been doing in the near future!
